======================================================================
Part 2: Normalized filling Ś f_p * 2^p / (p+1)! = s_p * C(n,p+1) / C(n,p+1) = s_p
If s_p ~ 2^p / (p+1)! then f_p ~ 1 (simplex-like)
If s_p > 2^p / (p+1)! then f_p > 1 (inflated)
======================================================================

